  "texts": [
    "ConclusionLeveraging the powerful learning capabilities of AI, intelligent ISAC is expected to facilitate the flexible and low-complexity network design and optimization under a dynamic environment, and has a great potential in enabling the diverse emerging applications for 5G.",
    "In this article, we provided a comprehensive survey on intelligent ISAC.",
    "First, we provided an overview of ISAC followed by its key techniques.",
    "Then, diverse AI techniques including ML, DL, DRL, FL, GAI, and TL were overviewed.",
    "In addition, we compared the model-based methods with the AI-based ones in system design and optimization for ISAC, discussing their advantages and disadvantages."
